{"tid":2074561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾徵費係林鄭周圍安監海康威視監控鏡的第一步","createTime":"2020-06-22T07:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T14:33:13.000Z","uid":26770,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"93d434d284195837833cbd6d1ff0269d97aef3b5","tid":2074561,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"港共就係想周圍有人扔垃圾<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下窮人區食都無錢一定周圍扔<br />\n林鄭就會話要保持衛生就要狂安監控鏡<br />\n<br />\n<ins>搵隊人凌晨去住宅區捉垃圾蟲,其實就係夾女示威者去強姦</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港警魔已經用ha 的系統搵有情緒病紀錄的人輪姦</span><br />\n荃灣x小姐就係其中一例, 爆左就屈你精神病發,刑事檢控專員豬狗不如梁卓然會誣告到你坐監"},{"pid":"5ea591eafc4507cb2deb26a4e17fc1c966f4befa","tid":2074561,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:53:11.000Z","msg":"難得因為經濟差同選舉近了<br />\n連帝制派都唔敢支持<br />\n<br />\n唔該民主派班智障咪再要求加會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2074539/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2074539/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7fa4d95f1f993c560b03d4660983c3ee435a5c9e","tid":2074561,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb40beecfd8a6dc3400efea0cbb51d9c6c1d8c9e","tid":2074561,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:56:26.000Z","msg":"冇計 wo<br />\n早年擴展堆填區又話爆又話臭又反對<br />\n起梵化爐環保團體又話空氣污染又反對"},{"pid":"8b880637ea003aaa7c00903ad65ee8c85daddfa4","tid":2074561,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"香港警魔連ha紀錄都偷,仲用作選擇目標強姦<br />\n<br />\n捉垃圾蟲的閉路唔直駁警魔總部我跟你姓"},{"pid":"f6460ef36b8b630451b45a64f05e3e77bca36437","tid":2074561,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:05:11.000Z","msg":"1984 既控制手段"},{"pid":"e2cb7db7b6d051ad3d8a44b7440755ec4d082e88","tid":2074561,"uid":47356,"like":0,"disl